   This repository consists of:

     * A build/install harness (install.sh, README.md, docs/) authored by
       the repository owner and released under Apache-2.0.

     * A set of source-file overlays under xrt-overlay/ derived from
       AMD/Xilinx XRT (https://github.com/Xilinx/XRT), which is itself
       licensed under Apache-2.0. Each overlay file carries the upstream
       copyright headers unchanged; local modifications add compatibility
       shims for Linux 6.8 -- 6.17 kernel API drift.

   The Apache-2.0 text is available at the URL above; a copy is not
   duplicated here to keep this file short. If you need a verbatim copy,
   see xrt-overlay/**/LICENSE or https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0.txt.
